<plot>Hoboken pizza-maker Federico Fellini, cousin to the famous director, attempts to fulfill his namesake's dying wish that a Fellini direct a film about Joan of Arc. This offbeat farcical comedy follows Fellini's attempts to find the perfect 'Joan' while keeping the film and his retirement years from falling apart.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?060659</url></doc>
